    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Genio <expan><abbr>signif</abbr><ex>erorum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXX <expan><abbr>U</abbr><ex>lpiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ictricis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Aelius Seve<lb break="no" n="4"/>rinus <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>oni</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Tafel gehört mit 2 weiteren zu einer fast kubischen Statuenbasis, die wahrscheinlich in den principia der Legionsfestung Vetera II stand.</p>
            </div>
